Zain Saudi Targets $2 Billion in Revenue in 2011, Seyassah Says

-- B y   F i o n a   M a c D o n a l d
-- 
2011-06-19T07:18:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-19/zain-saudi-targets-2-billion-in-revenue-in-2011-seyassah-says.html
Zain  Saudi Arabia , a unit of
 Kuwait ’s Mobile Telecommunications Co., is targeting revenue of
$2 billion this year,  Al-Seyassah  reported, citing Chief
Executive Officer Saad al-Barrak.  The company’s investment in Saudi Arabia reached $8 billion
with a share of more than 18 percent in the kingdom’s
telecommunications market, al-Barrak said, according to the
Kuwaiti newspaper.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Fiona MacDonald in Kuwait at 
